nodes.text: "Vulnerable Areas" is a comic strip written by Martin Fisher, drawn by Bob Molesworth and edited by Gunther Nickel. The story was published in the seventeenth issue of the Star Wars Rebels Magazine series by Egmont UK Ltd, which was released on April 20, 2016.
According to Fisher, the story takes place between the Star Wars Rebels episodes "The Future of the Force" and "Legacy."
